{"article_id":"sGbLr77A6uN4LbUe","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"LISTEN TO ARTICLE 6:06","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"SHARE THIS ARTICLE","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"Share Tweet","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Post Email","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"President Donald Trump flew halfway around the world for his hastily arranged second summit with North Korea ' s Kim Jong Un ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"betting","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"that his personal diplomacy could overcome sticking points","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"both sides have known about for years .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"The collapse of talks in Hanoi exposed just how far apart the adversaries are , even after two face-to-face meetings .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"Kim refused to walk away from his nuclear program","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"-- something","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"the regime has resisted for decades .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"Instead , he offered up one aging nuclear facility","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"but refused to give up his arsenal and other infrastructure --","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"while asking the U.S. to drop all of its sanctions .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Even Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"who ' s been eager for a deal ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"knew","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"he couldn ' t go that far .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"\" It was about the sanctions --","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"basically they wanted the sanctions lifted in their entirety","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"and we couldn ' t do that , \"","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Trump told reporters at a news conference Thursday in Hanoi","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"after talks were abruptly cut short .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"\" There is a gap .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"We have to have sanctions","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"and he wants to denuke ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"but he wants to do areas","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"that are less important","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"than we want . \"","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"Read a QuickTake on what you need to know about North Korea sanctions","depth":4},{"id":31,"text":"The president ' s move will be a relief to arms control experts","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"worried","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that Trump was willing to take a bad deal over no agreement .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"He arrived in Vietnam under pressure","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"to come away with more than the largely symbolic handshakes and vaguely worded joint statement of his first summit in Singapore eight months ago .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"But the path forward now is murky .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"While Trump and Secretary of State Michael Pompeo pledged to continue negotiations ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"it ' s unclear how North Korea will react to the president walking away from the bargaining table .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"And it casts fresh doubt on his strategy","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"of relying on top-down talks with the North Korean leader","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"to extract concessions .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"\" In a normal process these agreements are supposed to be pre-baked by negotiating teams","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"and then merely warmed-up","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"and served to the public by leaders for a photo-op , \"","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"said Sokeel Park of Liberty in North Korea , a human rights group","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that helps North Korean refugees .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"Despite North Korea arguably being at the top of Trump ' s list of foreign policy priorities ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"he gave his senior negotiator , State Department envoy Stephen Biegun , only a few weeks to try to hammer out details of an accord","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"that had eluded successive U.S. administrations for decades .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Among the possible options for agreement were decisions","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"to open liaison offices in Pyongyang and Washington ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"provide a full inventory of North Korea ' s nuclear stockpiles or open weapons facilities to international inspectors .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"But none of that materialized ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"with the the White House scratching a pre-advertised `` signing ceremony \" for the two leaders","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"as the talks unraveled .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Trump ' s willingness","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"to go home","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"without an accord","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"was the right move ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"according to Joel Wit , a North Korea expert at the Stimson Center","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"who helped negotiate an earlier accord with Pyongyang .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"\" This is negotiating 101 , \"","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"Wit said .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"\" He decided to up the ante","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"and put more pressure on Pyongyang","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"to get a better deal . \"","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"While Biegun has argued","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"that any agreement could take a long time ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"the breakdown was also a brutal example of the dangers","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"inherent in Trump ' s decision-by-instinct , top-down approach .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Read More :","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Trump Says","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"He Walked Out on Kim","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"After U.S . Demands Rejected","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Trump and Pompeo repeatedly said","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"they had been close to an agreement ,","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"but just couldn ' t get there this time .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"Grabbing what he has long called one of his signature achievements","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"in reaching out to North Korea ,","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"Trump said","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"Kim had assured him","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"that a freeze","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"in testing ballistic missiles and nuclear devices would continue .","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"Yet Trump also said ,","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"while sitting next to Kim ,","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"that there ' s \" no rush \"","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"to reach a broader deal .","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"That appeared to wash away any sense of urgency","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"that Kim agree to concrete steps toward denuclearization .","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"The question now is what comes next .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"Pompeo insisted","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"negotiations would continue ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"though he added","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"that it might be a \" little while \"","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"before that happens .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"\" We ' ll each need to regroup a little bit , \"","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"the top U.S. diplomat told reporters on his plane en route to Manila from Hanoi .","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"\" Look , there has to be a reason for the conversations .","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"There has to be a theory of the case","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"about how to move forward .","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"I ' m confident","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"that there is one . \"","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"Kim goes home without a deal , too ,","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"but he does so","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"after again winning legitimacy on the world stage ,","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"having gone toe-to-toe with an American president for the second time .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"Trump even said","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"military exercises with South Korea , long a source of frustration for Pyongyang , would remain suspended , in part due to their \" $ 100 million \" price tag .","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"Despite the abrupt end ,","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"there were extraordinary moments during the two-day summit","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"that suggested","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"the two sides are becoming more at ease .","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"In a remarkable first , Kim answered questions from journalists at the start of his meeting with Trump .","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"Asked","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"if he was ready to denuclearize ,","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"Kim responded","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"that he wouldn ' t have been in Hanoi","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"if he wasn ' t .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"Time","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"for that to happen under Trump ' s watch","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"is getting shorter by the day .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"The 2020 election is about 20 months away ,","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"and North Korea will almost certainly slow-walk any talks","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"as that date approaches","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"and it gauges whether Trump will win a second term","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"or be replaced by a Democrat","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"who may take a tougher approach .","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"As in past summits , Trump ' s meetings with Kim were overshadowed by events back home .","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"This time it was congressional testimony by Michael Cohen , Trump ' s former lawyer and fixer ,","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"who called the president a \" con man ' ' and a \" cheat. \"","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"That prompted the president to fire back","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"that the man","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"who once had an office next to his in Trump Tower","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"was \" lying","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"in order to reduce his prison time. \"","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"At the news conference Trump criticized the fact","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"that the hearing took place","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"while he was trying to negotiate with North Korea .","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"Before heading to Hanoi ' s airport ,","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"Trump and Pompeo put their best spin on the talks ,","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"they had made progress .","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"As he often does ,","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"Trump spoke in glowing terms of the North Korean leader and the relationship","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"they ' ve established .","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"\" Kim Jong Un is quite a guy and quite a character , \"","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"the president said .","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"\" There ' s tremendous potential in North Korea","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"and I think","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"he ' s going to lead it to a very important thing economically .","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"We just like each other . \"","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"Analysts","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"watching from the sidelines","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"dispensed with the personal praise ,","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"but conceded","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"that a breakdown was better than a bad deal .","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"Michael Green , a former Asia director for the National Security Council under President George W. Bush","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"who is now with the Center for Strategic and International Studies in Washington ,","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"said","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"he was worried","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"Trump might agree to pull some of the 30,000 U.S. troops from South Korea as a concession to Kim .","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"That didn ' t happen .","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"- With assistance by Youkyung Lee , Jihye Lee , and Jon Herskovitz","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":327,"left":0,"right":326,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent